Really f-ing simple.

1. Install jekyll [https://github.com/mojombo/jekyll/wiki/install"]
2. Create a new directory
3. Add this code
4. Run the jekyll server [https://github.com/mojombo/jekyll/wiki/usage]
5. Navigate to http://localhost:3000/"
6. Customize and enjoy (especially with github pages[http://pages.github.com/])